<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Aula marcada</title>
  <style>
    @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Athiti:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700&family=Lato:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,700;1,900&family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,900&display=swap");
    @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Athiti:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700&family=Electrolize&family=Fira+Sans:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Gotu&family=Lato:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,900&family=PT+Sans+Narrow:wght@400;700&display=swap");
    @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Athiti:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700&family=Electrolize&family=Fira+Sans:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Gotu&family=Lato:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,900&family=PT+Sans+Narrow:wght@400;700&display=swap");

    p {
      font-family: "Lato", sans-serif;
      color: #111;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: #5ac116;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: "Athiti", sans-serif;
      color: #5ac116;
      position: relative;
      -webkit-text-stroke: 1px black;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: "Athiti", sans-serif;
      color: #5ac116;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 200px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .eagle {
      width: 30px;
      height: auto;
      display: inline;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .box-comment {
      background-color: #ddd;
      font-style: italic;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <h1>
    Lembre-se da sua aula no dia <%= date %> às <%= time %>, <%= name %>!
  </h1>
  <p>
    Sua aula de inglês está marcada para <%= date %> às <%= time %>! Lembre-se
        de fazer seu homework e chegar na aula com o Anki vazio, pois tudo vale
        pontos!
  </p>
  <h2>Comentários do Professor:</h2>
  <div class="box-comment">
    <p>
      <%= description %>
    </p>
  </div>
  <p>
    Clique
    <a href="<%=link %>" target="_blank">aqui</a>
    para acessar a aula!
  </p>
  <p>Te vejo na aula!</p>
  <p>Teacher Arthur!</p>

  <h1>Remember your class on <%= date %>, <%= name %>!</h1>
  <p>
    Your English class is scheduled for <%= date %> at <%= time %>! Remember
        to do your homework and get to class with Anki empty, because everything
        is worth points!
  </p>
  <h2>Teacher's Comments:</h2>
  <div class="box-comment">
    <p>
      <%= description %>
    </p>
  </div>
  <p>
    Click
    <a href="<%=link %>" target="_blank">here</a>
    to access the class!
  </p>
  <p>See you in class!</p>
  <p>Teacher Arthur!</p>
  <img class="logo" src="https://ik.imagekit.io/vjz75qw96/assets/mylogotransp.png?updatedAt=1715968430436"
    alt="arvinlogo" />
</body>

</html>